                     <interp inst="t18260914-461-person2370" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I lodge at Cragg's. I heard her cry out, ran up, and saw the prisoner; the coat and breeches laid by his side. I found three keys on a ledge on the stairs.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18260914-461-person2371">
