            . I took him in charge with the property; the keys fit three locks in the house.(Property produced and sworn to).</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I went to inquire if one Courtney lodged there.</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182609140170"></xptr>MRS. CRAGG. He did not inquire for anybody - I found the room door unlocked, and the drawer stood open.</p>
